edu.ucla.sspace.graph.isomorphism

Class TypedIsomorphicGraphIndexer<T,G extends Multigraph<T,? extends TypedEdge<T>>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ucla.sspace.graph.isomorphism.TypedIsomorphicGraphIndexer<T,G>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Indexer<G>, Serializable, Iterable<Map.Entry<G,Integer>>

    public class TypedIsomorphicGraphIndexer<T,G extends Multigraph<T,? extends TypedEdge<T>>>
extends Object
implements Indexer<G>, Serializable
    An indexer that records only indices for non-isomorphic Multigraph instances. That is, if two multigraphs are isomorphic, they are mapped to the same index.
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
